import React from "react";
import {Container,Form,Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
const TelaLogin = () =>{
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Usuário:</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" name="user" id="user"></Form.Control>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Usuário:</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="password" name="pswd" id="pswd"></Form.Control>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button varianty="success">Acessar</Button>
                </Form>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default TelaLogin
